snippet.title: Instant Besan Halwa in 15 Mins - No Soak, No Grind with Tips & Tricks | Danedar Besan Ka Halwa
snippet.description:
full recipe: https://hebbarskitchen.com/besan-halwa-recipe-besan-ka-halwa/

@hebbarskitchenhindi @hebbarskitchenoriginals 

Besan Halwa Recipe | Besan Ka Halwa Recipe | Besan Ka Sheera with detailed photo and video recipe. A classic Indian dessert recipe made with chickpea flour, ghee and sugar. it is perhaps one of the most sought Indian sweet recipes made especially during festival seasons or for any particular occasion. It is easy and simple to make as compared to any other besan sweet like laddu and can be made in minutes.

Besan Halwa Recipe | Besan Ka Halwa Recipe | Besan Ka Sheera with step-by-step photo and video recipe. Halwa recipes are very common across India and are made with different ingredients. Basically, it is a dense sweet which can be either shaped as cubes or perhaps as dense powder. One such popular halwa recipe is the besan ka halwa recipe with the goodness of besan, ghee and also myriad dry fruit options.
